quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  88,1,"Have you heard tell [Prophet] about the Overwhelming Event?"
  88,2,"On that Day, there will be downcast faces,"
  88,3,"toiling and weary,"
  88,4,"as they enter the blazing Fire"
  88,5,"and are forced to drink from a boiling spring,"
  88,6,"with no food for them except bitter dry thorns"
  88,7,"that neither nourish nor satisfy hunger."
  88,8,"On that Day there will also be faces radiant with bliss,"
  88,9,"well pleased with their labour,"
  88,10,"in a lofty garden,"